{"id": 1401, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些被赋予仪式感的东西，你其实已经不想买账了？", "description": "你们演你们的，我就一边儿看看。（题图来自：David J. McMillan）", "record_count": 23524, "comment_count": 55, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201612221058310QGAnEI7c3zJbWF5.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-25T17:00:46Z", "questions": [{"id": 1571, "title": "哪些被赋予仪式感的东西，你其实已经不想买账了？", "content": "哪些被赋予仪式感的东西，你其实并不想买账？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 146130, "content": "结婚一定要有“一颗恒久远”的天然钻石，我不想买", "image": "img/option/option/20161222110618lfydXC57tJxRzgDc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 146155, "content": "毕业、换工作、度蜜月一定要出去旅游一场！…我不想去", "image": "img/option/option/20161222122213XzcebHaUGvCPEQSp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 146178, "content": "旅游城市必去的XX个景点、必尝的XX种美食，疲倦", "image": "img/option/option/20161222123114vYwQrV6DCTSO1BtH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 146141, "content": "平安夜圣诞节怎么能在家？要出去party啊！我不想去", "image": "img/option/option/20161222111650iyOu8bDFgXKTvWqS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 146185, "content": "新年到了，购入健身卡/手帐/书籍激励自己，骗自己啊", "image": "img/option/option/20161222120021m4wYJPeU3lZuGvXA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 146164, "content": "每次搬家，一定要搞些“租房也是家”式布置。屡试屡败，累", "image": "img/option/option/20161225185011wk584luh0b2yzgSX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 146134, "content": "男人一定要为自己选一块有档次的表，我不想买", "image": "img/option/option/20161222111110BDdHaq1mXMsyAEkL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}